lead_paragraph: Italy broke a 22-year hoodoo to end Spain's bid for a record third successive European title with a deserved 2-0 win over familiar foes in an absorbing last 16 clash between the two heavyweights at Euro 2016 on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Italy Breaks Jinx to End Spain's Long European Reign
